room_title: Escape room "Fenn's Cabin" by Jackson Escape Rooms in Jackson
review: The escape rooms sound amazing and I cannot wait to try them out.

room_title: Escape room "Fenn's Cabin" by Jackson Escape Rooms in Jackson
review: We've played a lot of escape rooms but Fenn's Cabin really stood out. We loved it! Awesome, well-designed games and friendly staff, we had a great time, thank you for having us!

room_title: Escape room "Fenn's Cabin" by Jackson Escape Rooms in Jackson
review: Being the veteran escape room enthusiasts my husband and I are, the Cabin escape room was one of the most challenging rooms ever. We loved the atmosphere and immersive feel the room had and the level of brain power it took to get through. Although we are disappointed we did not escape, we are very satisfied with the Jackson Escape Rooms and can't wait for our next visit. The staff were extremely knowledgeable, helpful, and are very receptive to feedback. We are excited to see what the other rooms hold as well what the amazing staff come up with next.

room_title: Escape room "Fenn's Cabin" by Jackson Escape Rooms in Jackson
review: Glad we have this in Jackson!! For the price of a movie and snacks, you can try something different and challenging. They are always changing the rooms so there is always something new to try. Just remember to get your confirmation email so you have a parking lot code for the gated parking lot.
